name: colexification
description: A command-line program to extract derivational morphology from raw lexical data and use these patterns to cluster related word forms.

name: COVID-19-Scholarly-Articles-Recommendation-Engine
description: This is a project based on the COVID-19 Open Research Dataset Challenge (CORD-19). We built a reccomendation engine using pyspark and spark-ml. This project utilizes Natural language processing and clustering techniques.
